## Technical Implementation Patterns

The system uses consistent URL routing patterns:
- Product areas: `/analytics/`, `/feature-experiment/`, `/data/`
- Chart types: `/analytics/charts/{chart-type}/`
- SDKs: `/sdks/{product}/{platform}/`
- APIs: `/apis/{product}/`
- Administrative: `/admin/{function}/`

Collections utilize mounting systems for content organization, with preview targets for content management, injection parameters for navigation context, and date-based content visibility controls. The platform supports both real-time and historical data analysis with configurable refresh intervals and maintains data integrity through deduplication algorithms and optimized caching mechanisms.